// Forgot Password process 
#1. User clicks on forgot Password
#2. Create a reset token (String) and save in the database.
#3. Send reset token to user email in the form of link.
#4. When user clicks on the link, compare the reset token 
    in the link with that saved in the database.
#5. If they match, then reset the user's password.

// Forgot password steps
#1. Create forgot password route.
#2. Create token model.
#3. Create email sender function (nodemailer).
#4. Create controller function.